## Anti-Patterns

- Monolithic "OrderService" that owns catalog, inventory, and payments
- Client-side price calculation trusted at payment
- Direct SQL joins across bounded context modules
- Synchronous Stripe calls inside database transactions
- Inventory decrement without prior reservation
- Order creation before payment confirmation (unless invoice flow approved)

